data.description: *Great buy on PCB, lowest priced home at this time*This end unit townhome on the East End of Panama City Beach will make a great first time home or a beach rental. It is convenient  to shopping and restaurants in either direction you go! The back yard is privacy fenced in with a side entry gate from road. There is no HOA's for this home.This home does need some TLC. Three buyers have backed out within 5-6 days with never seeing it in person, the only inspection done was a Termite Inspection and that was clear. The drywall in kitchen and soffit in the rear of home have been fixed. BEST deal on the beach right now!
